query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_records,
  AVG(priceYen) as avg_price_yen,
  AVG(priceYen) / 10000 as avg_price_man,
  MIN(priceYen) / 10000 as min_price_man,
  MAX(priceYen) / 10000 as max_price_man
FROM transactions
WHERE prefecture = '神奈川県' 
  AND city = '横浜市中区' 
  AND propertyType = 'マンション';
